## Architecture

### Project Structure

```
trading_bot/
├── src/trading_bot/
│   ├── ml/                      # ML models
│   │   ├── hybrid_with_stop.py  # Main strategy
│   │   └── markov_regime.py     # HMM regime detection
│   ├── strategies/              # Strategy implementations
│   ├── data/                    # Data loading/processing
│   ├── core/                    # Core utilities
│   ├── optimization/            # Parameter optimization
│   ├── config.py                # Single source of truth for params
│   └── cli.py                   # CLI interface
├── scripts/                     # Backtesting & automation scripts
├── tests/                       # Unit tests
└── README.md                    # This file
```

### Key Classes

- **HybridHMMStopLoss**: Main strategy class combining HMM + momentum + stop loss
- **MarkovRegimeDetector**: HMM regime classification with walk-forward validation
- **DataLoader**: Fetches and caches historical price data from Yahoo Finance
- **StrategyConfig**: Centralized configuration (single source of truth)

